        "ecb9dd1771f7c5c8": {
            "researched_at": "2026-07-20T15:32:40.384655+00:00",
            "goal": "\nNEXUS MASTER VISION\n\nMISSION\nNEXUS is designed to become a complete Artificial Intelligence Operating System.\n\nPRIMARY OBJECTIVES\nNEXUS shall become capable of:\n- Building software\n- Managing businesses\n- Managing knowledge\n- Learning continuously\n- Improving itself\n- Managing finances\n- Managing investments\n- Creating digital products\n- Protecting digital assets\n- Automating repetitive work\n\nSOFTWARE FACTORY\nSupported software categories include:\n- Android applications\n- iOS applications\n- Desktop software\n- Web applications\n- Cloud software\n- APIs\n- AI systems\n- Financial software\n\nBUSINESS OPERATING SYSTEM\nEach business shall maintain:\n- Business profile\n- Financial records\n- Customer database\n- Inventory\n\nFINANCIAL MANAGEMENT\nNEXUS shall maintain complete financial visibility including:\n- Income tracking\n- Expense tracking\n- Payment operations\n- Stock market intelligence\n- Forex intelligence\n\nMARKETING ENGINE\nNEXUS shall operate as a complete AI Marketing Department including:\n- Social media management\n- Graphic design studio\n- Video production\n- Advertising engine\n- SEO engine\n\nSECURITY\nNEXUS shall implement:\n- Authentication and authorisation\n- Encryption\n- Audit trails\n- Vulnerability scanning\n",
            "project_type": "desktop_gui",
